Date: Tue, 3 Feb 2026 22:03:51 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 23/28] make APB and AXI4 delayer both use Config.delayratio
 direct connect when ratio==1

---
 src/Top.scala              |   1 +
 src/amba/APBDelayer.scala  | 146 +++++++++++++-------------
 src/amba/AXI4Delayer.scala | 203 ++++++++++++++++++++-----------------
 3 files changed, 186 insertions(+), 164 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/Top.scala b/src/Top.scala
